        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Sorry, I just noticed a reference to "bane" spells above, to clear up the misconception on bane spells, there are 2 bane spells for wizzies, both take ooposite faction to acquire, as do most things in velious, and both work on a very select few mob's which in turn require a "uber" guild to raid, I am not even going to waste my time getting these spells as they are such a joke, velious is not meant for wizards at all, our best spell in my opinion is and will always be ice comet, next to useless in velious, kinda silly isn't it?<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
